new_feature_requests.summary: Make the "Get Started" button open the provided Google Forms URL when tapped

Update the Landing Page hero section “Get Started” button so that tapping/clicking it opens this URL: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfPd7k1jiJqI71faIie9aYOmeScqdQ98jTcIFtYoJK9AJvHig/viewform?usp=preview (open in a new browser tab/window) instead of triggering the Internet Identity login flow.
